{"tid":2341444,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"而家香港係咪唔分着 著","createTime":"2020-12-26T11:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T18:48:38.000Z","uid":118628,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"411bb083101761ecb06c26733a148dd7f242604c","tid":2341444,"uid":118628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:08:53.000Z","msg":"以前分得好清楚<br />\n著，著名 著作<br />\n着，着火 着衫 着想 衣着<br />\n而家好似統一用晒著<br />\n係咪同速成倉頡 電腦編碼有關？"},{"pid":"f9aeb0db6f47cb8b311bf02f78de86825070a645","tid":2341444,"uid":118628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/07/04/KHzRoi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F07%2F04%2FKHzRoi.png&h=52e73084&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4d9c67cc2c1c8b41b6a5b2e837197b3aea18099","tid":2341444,"uid":149041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"411bb083101761ecb06c26733a148dd7f242604c","tid":2341444,"uid":118628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:08:53.000Z","msg":"以前分得好清楚<br />\n著，著名 著作<br />\n着，着火 着衫 着想 衣着<br />\n而家好似統一用晒著<br />\n係咪同速成倉頡 電腦編碼有關？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:14:20.000Z","msg":"而家啲電腦好似有返着字啦？"},{"pid":"35f8fb7097fef69ad2c4bdc8902c124c90484c77","tid":2341444,"uid":33373,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:14:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://jonathanovsky.wordpress.com/2015/03/12/%E3%80%8C%E7%9D%80%E3%80%8D%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8C%E8%91%97%E3%80%8D%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjonathanovsky.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F03%2F12%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%259D%2580%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%2592%258C%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%2591%2597%25E3%2580%258D%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%2588%25A5%2F&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=8bec70ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jonathanovsky.wordpress.com/2015/03/12/%E3%80%8C%E7%9D%80%E3%80%8D%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8C%E8%91%97%E3%80%8D%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%A5/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n換言之，無論「着」還是「著」查實都是由「箸」譌變而成的，香港的慣常用法，是將「着」當作「著」的派生字，將二字分家以消除歧義。「着」粵音有二讀，「穿着」、「着火」這類詞語【zoek3】，「着落」、「着手」時則讀【zoek6】；「著」則用作「著作」或「著名」之意，音【zyu3】。<br />\n由於台灣官方只接納「著」為正體，把「着」視作異體，因此他們只有一個寫法，意思上的差異則只用發音來分。「穿著」、「著落」讀【zhu&oacute;】;「著凉」、「著火」讀【zh&aacute;o】；成語「棋差一著」讀【zhāo】；「著作」、「著名」時讀【zh&ugrave;】，當動詞用如「走着」時，則讀【zhe】。"},{"pid":"1e73b034480f57a0e67519b91684323f259e013a","tid":2341444,"uid":96439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9aeb0db6f47cb8b311bf02f78de86825070a645","tid":2341444,"uid":118628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/07/04/KHzRoi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F07%2F04%2FKHzRoi.png&h=52e73084&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:15:30.000Z","msg":"高登文化冇左好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19f785d3646dd7774d301d18a866e50486ec14a","tid":2341444,"uid":118628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"35f8fb7097fef69ad2c4bdc8902c124c90484c77","tid":2341444,"uid":33373,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:14:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://jonathanovsky.wordpress.com/2015/03/12/%E3%80%8C%E7%9D%80%E3%80%8D%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8C%E8%91%97%E3%80%8D%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjonathanovsky.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F03%2F12%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%259D%2580%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%2592%258C%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%2591%2597%25E3%2580%258D%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%2588%25A5%2F&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=8bec70ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jonathanovsky.wordpress.com/2015/03/12/%E3%80%8C%E7%9D%80%E3%80%8D%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8C%E8%91%97%E3%80%8D%E4%B9%8B%E5%88%A5/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n換言之，無論「着」還是「著」查實都是由「箸」譌變而成的，香港的慣常用法，是將「着」當作「著」的派生字，將二字分家以消除歧義。「着」粵音有二讀，「穿着」、「着火」這類詞語【zoek3】，「着落」、「着手」時則讀【zoek6】；「著」則用作「著作」或「著名」之意，音【zyu3】。<br />\n由於台灣官方只接納「著」為正體，把「着」視作異體，因此他們只有一個寫法，意思上的差異則只用發音來分。「穿著」、「著落」讀【zhu&oacute;】;「著凉」、「著火」讀【zh&aacute;o】；成語「棋差一著」讀【zhāo】；「著作」、「著名」時讀【zh&ugrave;】，當動詞用如「走着」時，則讀【zhe】。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:15:42.000Z","msg":"而家網上世界<br />\n好多人只用著<br />\n<br />\n歌詞好多都係著"},{"pid":"a9453168052ed05199cc98c3dbd942b9474337b9","tid":2341444,"uid":153311,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:15:56.000Z","msg":"曾經有段時間係因為打字出唔到着，所以先着著通用，但而家既然出到就應該要分清楚"},{"pid":"c8c343e654ca6a8265e7a0990bbef6638a8f709c","tid":2341444,"uid":228337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:18:55.000Z","msg":"以前啲正體中文輸入法都係台灣中文<br />\n久而久之用咗台灣嗰套"},{"pid":"a5cf90ea0445532b853d085ce449691881ba034e","tid":2341444,"uid":118628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:19:04.000Z","msg":"還記得櫻花正開 還未懂跟你示愛<br />\n初春來時 彼此閉著眼 渴望未來"},{"pid":"293bcf2f1a264224ee4cceb8c5156d93da729c3d","tid":2341444,"uid":231705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:20:20.000Z","msg":"電腦速成個着字要成6下空白先揾到隻字我諗d人情願打著都唔會打着字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ea95e76b358a92b6d0733b5157ba7caf270a53","tid":2341444,"uid":118628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a9453168052ed05199cc98c3dbd942b9474337b9","tid":2341444,"uid":153311,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:15:56.000Z","msg":"曾經有段時間係因為打字出唔到着，所以先着著通用，但而家既然出到就應該要分清楚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:20:26.000Z","msg":"我相信同臺灣有關<br />\n臺灣統一一個著字<br />\n但你留意下<br />\n香港好多歌詞<br />\n明明應該用着，但用左著"},{"pid":"84bac83c0a980efbeb18cc1416d90327550c1cba","tid":2341444,"uid":54528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:21:00.000Z","msg":"用電腦打字都無個着字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor